{"tid":1070657,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【祖國窮富翁大作戰】富二代首次洗碗：「好噁心！」","createTime":"2019-03-20T22:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T00:43:57.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65cf99ecb6c710b4d6e42162de892ebc2fabccc2","tid":1070657,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T22:47:53.000Z","msg":"24歲的富二代納維德（Navid）經常出入名流圈子。他獨愛Versace，由全身衣物、床鋪被鋪以至用餐碟子都是這品牌的出品，當然其他名牌如Gucci和Fendi的手袋鞋子也不缺少。他參加英國電視台節目「Channel 5」節目《富小孩變窮》（Rich Kids Go Skint），才首次見識「貼地」生活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節目中納維德首次入廚房，幫窮家庭準備午餐以及洗碗，而他最擔心的，竟是被髒水沾污名牌衣服，他表示︰「這是我首次洗碗，我感到雙手怪怪的，真的好噁心，我之後要搽保濕霜，以免雙手太乾。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n納維德曾表示︰「我從來沒有開支預算的，我一定會得到財政支持。如果我見到漂亮、我需要的東西，我便購買。」他在這次體驗中首次見識到如何用50英鎊（約500港幣）買一周所需的食物，也首次學到「講價」的技巧。"},{"pid":"b52248266fb36c5fb63fa2b24f8ee8b5cc807efe","tid":1070657,"uid":101110,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T22:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sL3BsfL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsL3BsfL.png&h=38bc57c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n24歲有錢仔嚟講都算樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVersace唔係個個著到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86800c0c35af161d1fd947c99ea53a3537079cba","tid":1070657,"uid":202464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sL3BsfL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsL3BsfL.png&h=38bc57c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n24歲有錢仔嚟講都算樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVersace唔係個個著到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算幾樣衰都好，都一定多女屌過窮既靚仔。"},{"pid":"d3f7a5243809505f47f372848ee6d52ff44ff9b1","tid":1070657,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86800c0c35af161d1fd947c99ea53a3537079cba","tid":107065